body: This happens regularly in our Travis test runs. It doesn't happen always due to threading non-determinism. Example of an error: https://travis-ci.org/TokTok/c-toxcore/jobs/175571271#L1620.

comment_data.body: https://travis-ci.org/TokTok/c-toxcore/jobs/184226203#L1677 it seems to still be an issue.
It is indeed still an issue in recent builds. CC: @pchk.
